{"tid":659540,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"中國球迷唔知鹿島喺邊 買機票去咗鹿兒島......","createTime":"2018-05-10T02:00:43.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-10T07:51:47.000Z","uid":39464,"like":43,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"e423518a145ba44b5fb683b02dc54246428b01a0","tid":659540,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-10T02:00:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180509/large/1525861680_53e6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180509%2Flarge%2F1525861680_53e6.jpg&h=7f5484b4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n鹿島鹿角主場迎戰上海上港嘅亞冠盃16強首回合而家就踢緊，不過同時間網絡就出現咗個關於今場比賽嘅「悲劇」，又話或可以話係笑話嘅。<br />\n<br />\n話說國內百度「中超吧」一位網名為「上体之王浩克」嘅網民為咗支持自己心愛嘅上港，決定今場親自飛去日本睇波，佢仲喺討論區上載咗自己行程嘅截圖，仲留言話「誰言上港無死忠？機票已訂，期待亞冠客場揚威！」<br />\n<br />\n上海上港今場能唔能夠「客場揚威」暫時就未知，不過都幾肯定呢位國內球迷應該冇辦法現場睇到呢場波，事關佢竟然以為鹿島鹿角係喺日本西南部嘅鹿兒島，買咗機票過去。係呢度提提大家，鹿島鹿角其實關東茨城縣嘅球會，同鹿兒島距離差好遠。事件仲傳到去日本，搞到班日本網民笑到碌地㖭。所以話，常識真係好重要㗎......<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.sports.appledaily.com/sports/realtime/article/20180509/58171854\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.sports.appledaily.com%2Fsports%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180509%2F58171854&d=3680jztEDHKTRDWNjPSfFcVakpCEQgWe3bOYm8oES40%3D&h=be886dd6\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.sports.appledaily.com%2Fsports%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180509%2F58171854&h=7f3f4268\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.sports.appledaily.com/sports/realtime/article/20180509/58171854</a>"},{"pid":"c2fe68987cb8b8c550d4494711a4c6c0a0655c21","tid":659540,"uid":15,"like":20,"dislike":0,"score":20,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-10T02:02:45.000Z","msg":"支那狗又搵新籍口去日本<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/do